<view class="page" wx:if="{{card}}">
 <view class="hero card">
  <text class="eyebrow">分享卡片</text>
  <view class="hero-title">{{card.petName}}</view>
  <view class="hero-code">{{card.code}} · {{card.personalityName}}</view>
  <view class="hero-subtitle">{{card.personalityTitle}}</view>
  <view class="tags">
   <text wx:for="{{card.traits}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text>
  </view>
 </view>

 <view class="card summary">
  <view class="section-title">分享摘要</view>
  <text>{{card.summary}}</text>
 </view>

 <view class="card dims">
  <view class="section-title">四维速览</view>
  <view class="dim" wx:for="{{card.dimensions}}" wx:key="label">
   <view class="between"><text class="dim-label">{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.value}}%</text></view>
   <view class="track"><view style="width:{{item.value}}%"></view></view>
  </view>
  <view class="fit">原型匹配度 {{card.fit}}%</view>
 </view>

 <view class="card tips">
  <view class="section-title">当前版本说明</view>
  <text>现在已经可以在小程序内预览分享内容，并通过原生转发把测试结果发给朋友。后续我们会继续补齐更精细的分享海报样式与云端能力。</text>
 </view>

 <view class="card poster-box">
  <view class="section-title">海报预览</view>
  <image wx:if="{{posterPath}}" src="{{posterPath}}" mode="widthFix" class="poster-preview"/>
  <view wx:elif="{{rendering}}" class="poster-loading">正在生成分享海报…</view>
  <view wx:else class="poster-loading">还没有生成海报</view>
 </view>

 <button class="primary action" open-type="share">立即分享</button>
 <button class="secondary action" bindtap="useSystemShare">打开分享菜单</button>
 <button class="secondary action" bindtap="savePoster">保存到相册</button>
 <button class="secondary action" bindtap="saveHint">查看保存说明</button>
 <canvas type="2d" id="sharePoster" class="hidden-canvas"></canvas>
</view>

<view class="page" wx:else>
 <view class="empty card">
  <text class="empty-title">还没有可预览的分享卡</text>
  <text>先在结果页或完整报告页点击“生成分享卡片”，再回来查看这里的内容。</text>
 </view>
</view>
